ActNorthwest Territories Act
SubjectRelinquishement of the administration and control from the Commissioner of Northwest Territories
PrecisOrder consenting to the RELINQUISHMENT in perpetuity, by the Commissioner of Northwest Territories, of the administration and control of the surface rights of the lands at the Cantung Exclusion Area in the Northwest Territories that were originally transferred to the Commissioner of Northwest Territories under the Northwest Territories Lands and Resources Devolution Transfer Agreement on April 1, 2014.
